Class OpcProjectBaseline

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.mpxj.opc.OpcProjectBaseline

  • public class OpcProjectBaseline
extends Object
    Represents a baseline in OPC when baselines for a project are listed, and used to request export of a baseline as part of a project export.
